@startuml Sequence_UC09
title UC-09: Membuat Pesanan dan Pembayaran

actor "Kasir" as User
participant "Halaman Buat Pesanan\n(livewire/transaction)" as View
participant "Transaction\\BuatPesanan\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Transaction Model" as TxModel
participant "TransactionDetail Model" as DetailModel
participant "Payment Model" as PaymentModel
participant "Production Model" as ProductionModel
participant "Notification Model" as NotifModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /kasir/buat-pesanan
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> DB: SELECT products (active), payment_channels, shifts (active)
DB --> Component: Data referensi
Component --> View: Tampil form pesanan

User -> View: Memilih metode (Reguler/Kotak/SiapBeli)
View -> Component: Set $method

User -> View: Menambahkan produk & jumlah
View -> Component: addItem($productId, $qty)
Component -> DB: SELECT products WHERE id = ?
DB --> Component: Product dengan harga & stok
Component -> Component: Hitung subtotal & grand total
Component --> View: Perbarui tampilan keranjang

User -> View: Isi nama pelanggan, nomor HP,\ntanggal ambil (untuk pesanan)
View -> Component: Set customer data

User -> View: Klik Proses Bayar
View -> Component: processPayment()
Component -> Component: validate(['items'=>'required|min:1', ...])
alt Tidak ada item
  Component --> View: Validasi gagal
else Berhasil
  Component -> TxModel: Transaction::create(['invoice_number'=>..., 'status'=>'Aktif', ...])
  TxModel -> DB: INSERT INTO transactions

  loop Setiap item pesanan
    Component -> DetailModel: TransactionDetail::create(['transaction_id'=>..., ...])
    DetailModel -> DB: INSERT INTO transaction_details
  end

  Component -> PaymentModel: Payment::create(['transaction_id'=>..., 'paid_amount'=>...])
  PaymentModel -> DB: INSERT INTO payments

  alt Metode bukan Siap Beli
    Component -> ProductionModel: Production::create(['transaction_id'=>..., ...])
    ProductionModel -> DB: INSERT INTO productions
    Component -> NotifModel: Notification::create(['type'=>'new_order',...])
    NotifModel -> DB: INSERT INTO notifications
  else Siap Beli
    Component -> DB: UPDATE products SET stock = stock - qty WHERE id = ?
    Component -> TxModel: $transaction->update(['status'=>'Selesai'])
    TxModel -> DB: UPDATE transactions
  end

  Component --> View: Redirect ke halaman struk
end

User -> View: Mencetak / mengunduh struk (opsional)

@enduml
